{"id":103350,"date":"2018-03-07T10:00:59","date_gmt":"2018-03-07T15:00:59","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/techvibes.com\/?p=103350"},"modified":"2018-05-29T14:30:05","modified_gmt":"2018-05-29T18:30:05","slug":"killer-spaces-broadbandtv-vancouver","status":"publish","type":"magazine","link":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/magazine\/killer-spaces-broadbandtv-vancouver","title":{"rendered":"BBTV Vancouver: The Castle that Content Built"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b>Every third Youtube video that you watch is associated with BBTV&#8230; mic drop.\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tens of thousands of content creators, 34 billion monthly impressions, 285 million unique viewers, 400 (<a href=\"https:\/\/jobs.techvibes.com\/broadbandtv\">and growing<\/a>) employees, and 23 internal departments; welcome to BroadbandTV aka BBTV. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shahrzad Rafati is BBTV&#8217;s Iranian-born founder who pioneered the business after seeing the distinct difference in access to content between her birthplace and her Canadian home of Vancouver. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Since launching in 2005 BBTV has been a leader in defining and advancing the digital video space.\u00a0 Today, BBTV\u00a0is the third largest video property in the world behind Facebook and Google.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">CEO Rafati was named\u00a0to Fast Company&#8217;s 100 Most Creative People in Business, and last month <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">took home the Entrepreneur of the Year award honours at the <a href=\"https:\/\/borndigital.com\/2018\/02\/23\/winners-of-the-seventh-annual-canadian-innovation-awards\">7th Annual Canadian Innovation Awards<\/a>.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103332\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-29.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -29\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-29.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-29-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-29-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-29-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-29-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Since 2005,\u00a0BBTV has empowered a new generation of storytellers and transformed entertainment in the way it is produced and consumed. YouTube, Netflix, Amazon, HuffPost, and the NBA are all BBTV partners. And it doesn\u2019t end there, BBTV\u2019s in-house brands have reputations of their own and include HooplaKidz, Opposition, WIMSIC, TGN, Outspeak, and NBA Playmakers.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With all these content producers working alongside each other, BBTV has built one of the strongest ecosystems in digital video worldwide. Last year total annual viewership for BBTV increased 66%, a milestone achievement for any team. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In 2017, the team moved into a new space, created in close collaboration with <a href=\"http:\/\/threexnine.com\/\">3&#215;9 Planning &amp; Design<\/a>, it\u2019s an office worth talking, nay vlogging, about.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><strong>Work<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>BBTV is a community of creativity; a network of partnerships, digital talent, content, and ideas. It\u2019s a theme that inspires much of the d\u00e9cor, like the Binary Wall, which is a translation of the company\u2019s name in binary code and constructed as a spatial pattern into a wall relief.<\/p>\n<p>The inspiration for it comes from Rafati, \u201cBehind every layer of the design is a code \u2013 a piece of the company\u2019s DNA \u2013 it\u2019s represented in the walls and art around the office and symbolizes our core values: Care, Drive, Collaboration, and Creativity.\u201d<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103347\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-2.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -2\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-2.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-2-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-2-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_103346\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-103346\" style=\"width: 1550px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-103346 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-5.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -5\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-5.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-5-730x487.jpg 730w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-5-1460x973.jpg 1460w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-5-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-5-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-5-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-5-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-103346\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Their workspaces are filled with custom-made hexagon crystalline lighting structures that are intended to inspire innovative and original thinking.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The BBTV team enjoys a variety of collaborative workstations, break out spaces, lounges and phone booths to ensure there is a space available for the task at hand.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103334\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-27.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -27\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-27.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-27-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-27-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-27-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-27-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103338\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-21.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -21\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-21.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-21-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-21-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-21-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-21-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103341\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-12.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -12\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-12.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-12-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-12-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-12-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-12-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103329\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-25.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -25\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-25.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-25-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-25-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-25-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-25-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Content is king &#8211; this notion goes undisputed at BBTV, and they\u00a0their spaces match that sentiment, including a 50-seat theatre built into the center of the office used for work and for play.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103339\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-16.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -16\" width=\"1549\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-16.jpg 1549w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-16-730x487.jpg 730w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-16-1460x974.jpg 1460w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-16-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-16-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-16-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-16-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-16-1280x854.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1549px) 100vw, 1549px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103340\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-17.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -17\" width=\"1549\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-17.jpg 1549w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-17-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-17-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-17-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-17-1280x854.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1549px) 100vw, 1549px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>Eat<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We all try to eat healthy but at BBTV, they take it up a notch. Their in-office caf\u00e9 is filled with \u201cBrain Food,\u201d which is a range of nourishment that follows a holistic approach and prioritizes wellness over diet. Although that doesn\u2019t mean they don\u2019t offer the usual goodies. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Coffee, tea, and healthy snacks, such as oatmeal, nuts, and vegetables, can be found in the kitchen on a daily basis.\u00a0<\/span>And since it\u2019s near impossible to celebrate TGIF without a little sugar, BBTV-ers can always count on ending the week with donuts and bagels from Rosemary Rocksalt.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103333\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-26.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -26\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-26.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-26-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-26-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-26-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-26-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Those who live by the words, \u201cBut first, coffee,\u201d can feel at home here. BBTV has an in-house automated barista and a number of organic roast options that are refilled and refreshed daily.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Because the office is located in Vancouver\u2019s Coal Harbour district, lunch and after-work places are abundant. Well within walking distance are a Starbucks, JJ Bean, Cactus Club, and Robson Street.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><strong>Culture<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>\u201cYou become what you believe\u201d has been at the end of Rafati\u2019s email signature since she started the business, and that sentiment echoes throughout their office and the company values.<\/p>\n<p>Internally, that belief takes shape in their commitment to maintaining equal pay and gender balance, as well as maternity and paternity programs. BBTV-ers are also entitled to four weeks\u2019 vacation, extended health benefits, free gym passes, and corporate discounts at Rogers, Mobi, Steve Nash Gyms, Oxygen, Sparkling Hill Resort, and Perkopolis.<\/p>\n<p>Once a year, employees can take a paid day off to volunteer for a charity, community event, or initiative they\u2019re passionate about. In the past, BBTV-ers have supported the Malala Fund, Kiva, Happy Herd, Dress for Success, and the Children\u2019s Wish Foundation.<\/p>\n<p>A grand piano sits in the lobby, free to play, free to experiment, and free to inspire. It represents the company\u2019s roots in music as well as their commitment to creativity, skill, knowledge, and art.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103349\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-1.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -1\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095642\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-1.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095642\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095642\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095642\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-1-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095642\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-1-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Custom murals and imagery featuring the\u00a0BBTV brands.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103337\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-20.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -20\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-20.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-20-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-20-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-20-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-20-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rafati started with a few plants in her office and now it\u2019s grown to 400. In the same week BBTV moved into their new space, the company turned 11 years old. If you add the total sum of the translation of BBTV11 as an ASCII code, you get the number 400, and that is no coincidence.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103336\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-22.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -22\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-22.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-22-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-22-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-22-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-22-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103330\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-30.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -30\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-30.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-30-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brains