pg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -9\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-9.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-9-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-9-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-9-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-9-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The Lounge is an environment filled with music \u2013 a place for thinking out loud and relaxing. Situated slightly removed from the central offices, it features Canadian artist Emily Filler, whose paintings are showcased here.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103348\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-3.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -3\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-3.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-3-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095644\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-3-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Extracurricular activities and clubs are the norm at BBTV. Collective interests include marathon running, theatre, ping pong, and community service with local organizations like the BC Children\u2019s Hospital.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Retreats, social outings, and parties are all organized by a committee that goes by the name of E.P.I.C. and whose mandate is to foster ideation and collaboration within the organization. They put together several annual events that are centered around developing ideas and solutions for business challenges as well as team building and engagement.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103331\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-28.jpg\" alt=\"Broadband TV Office Killer Spaces -28\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-28.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-28-730x487.jpg 730w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-28-1460x973.jpg 1460w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-28-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-28-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-28-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-28-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/03\/13095645\/Broadband-TV-Office-Killer-Spaces-28-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><em>Do you have an amazing office and would like to be featured here? Get in touch with us: contact@techvibes.com.<\/em><\/p>\n